{"tid":1684258,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【打擊共媒】Twitter宣布下月起全面禁止政治廣告","createTime":"2019-10-31T04:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T04:20:39.000Z","uid":69597,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef06efd9d39ff97c2136a3ac8f4e77764be9e57","tid":1684258,"uid":69597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】社交網站Twitter宣布，將全面禁止在網站內的所有政治廣告。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter行政總裁多爾西發文表示，網站決定由下月22日起，全面禁止所有政治廣告，他解釋指涉及政治理念的訊息，不應透過支付金錢賣廣告，作為傳遞及散播的媒介。<br />\n<br />\n他又指網絡廣告對商戶而言是非常強大而有效的宣傳方式，但作為政治宣傳則存在重大風險，可以左右數以百萬計選票流向。他又指網絡政治廣告對現代公民社會帶來新挑戰，因為未經證實的資訊可以透過網絡以快速、複雜及難以抵擋的方式傳播，導致出現不公平情況。<br />\n<br />\n他重申Twitter一直致力阻止用戶傳播誤導性資訊，但如果有關資訊以廣告形式出現，則難以把關。他又強調這次決定與言論自由無關，市場預料全面禁止政治廣告，將不會對Twitter收入造成太大影響，而Twitter股價在開市後下跌約百分之1.9。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=368174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368174&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA8hAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=a2d6af62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368174&h=f0f94287\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=368174</a><br />\n<br />\n幫支那慳維穩費<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385540b76e9c4a871f0b4ee4344b54a235cc743e","tid":1684258,"uid":80200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:11:28.000Z","msg":"Twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17803271313398c7501a25e73a3e7228100ffda6","tid":1684258,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:15